title: Ted Budd Wins North Carolina Senate Seat
description: Ted Budd defeated the Democrat, Cheri Beasley, to capture the seat of the retiring Republican, Senator Richard Burr.
dc:creator: Jonathan Weisman
media:credit: Logan R. Cyrus for The New York Times
media:description: Representative Ted Budd of North Carolina, who voted against certifying the 2020 presidential election, ran a low-key race.
